summary: CONSUMER CALLED COMPLAINING ABOUT HAVING PROBLEMS WITH COSCO  MODEL # 02-880-EBN, DOM 01-20 2002. CONSUMER STATED HARNESS DID NOT OPERATE PROPERLY.
